ing: 1 tablespoon fresh lime juice, or to taste
1 teaspoon sea salt, or to taste
1 1/2 large ripe avocados, pitted and peeled
des: "Serve with dippers. Keeps well, tightly covered, in the fridge for 1 to 3 days."
ins: Place chickpeas, water, tahini, lime juice, salt, garlic, and cumin in a food processor. Puree until smooth, about 2 minutes. Add avocados, spinach, and olive oil; puree until creamy, 2 to 3 minutes.
